    <item>
      <title>中国输出通货紧缩但美国并未受益</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-12/china-exports-deflation-but-us-isn-t-benefiting-as-ties-weaken</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在美国及其盟友谴责中国工业“产能过剩”并准备提高关税作为回应的同时，那些将工厂与世界联系起来的国家正在为抑制通胀做出努力。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-12/china-exports-deflation-but-us-isn-t-benefiting-as-ties-weaken</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 12 Jun 2024 06:00:01 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美国原油和汽油库存增加导致油价回吐涨幅</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-11/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-june-12</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国政府数据显示，该国原油库存意外增加，抑制了此前因通胀压力降温而推动的涨势，随后油价缩减涨幅，至每桶 78 美元附近。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-11/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-june-12</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 11 Jun 2024 23:25:31 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
